Silverbolt and Torca stood watching as the operation was taking place
in the next room, observing as the doctors worked frantaically to keep
both of thier patients alive. Then finally there was a change.

"Look at that!" Bantor who had turned back to watch could see that
Rodimus' vital signs were getting stronger. Tuscon's were also showing
strength and vitality, seemingly alomost in unison with Rodimus'

Silverbolt smiled, "Rodimus will vanquish all the enemies before him."
There was a proud smile on his face as he watched.
